      ],
      "sc:description": "Franken is a method for efficient and accurate molecular dynamics simulations that enhances the accuracy of atomistic foundation models. It extends the MEKRR method to fit both energies and forces, enabling feasible MD simulations and offering a fast and practical solution for training potentials.",
